# Large data files that should NOT be committed via plain git
# (use git-lfs or a Zenodo deposit for these):
#   Results/test_suite/sNN__*/samples.csv  may be tens to hundreds of MB each;
#   the .csv glob is left UN-ignored so smaller summary CSVs (e.g. nmcmc_sweep_summary.csv)
#   still commit normally. Add explicit paths here when populating Results/.
